{"tid":1485322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我死都唔割架喇！","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:06:42.000Z","uid":105505,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f6fba06ff570f58baa2866ec74b97f422411aa","tid":1485322,"uid":105505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"話左唔割就唔割，但係都希望前線手足可以走。<br />\n今日大家都講好左一齊翻屋企食飯，媽媽等緊你地翻去！<br />\n我地今日其實好成功，各界都無位入我地，無得叫我地做暴徒，唔係警民衝突，我地係和平集會。今日係和理非嘅主場，希望勇武都可以尊重翻和理非。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"89425f8897be8118e51b5ae3999dbf10caf4fb9e","tid":1485322,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:49:58.000Z","msg":"前線唔駛叫人走，你要走左先，人少左就無留低理由<br />\n<br />\n每位巴絲麻煩各發一個貼， 要連登頭版都係依個caption"},{"pid":"754825fb3ed73b88586477fa2064a434e85bc372","tid":1485322,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"無曬狗出黎講野/佈防，仲未知唔對路？<br />\n返屋企啦！！<br />\n留得青山在，哪怕無春袋.比你錫"},{"pid":"519923bc5194cf13c3422c3c7999bb7784171c4c","tid":1485322,"uid":79039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:50:00.000Z","msg":"170 萬人集會之後係Deadline呀！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1484416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1484416</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n返屋企做文宣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非&gt;Deadline&gt;行動升級</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"f0eb66ad485cc7c1635dd3e20b7115ec8760f265","tid":1485322,"uid":14171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f3e820683af3ae0e1eeed4af9fb79060c61ad70","tid":1485322,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:50:10.000Z","msg":"死都唔割"},{"pid":"d83b04a67d2b1466b0f623cd1b923b5263f9457c","tid":14853